        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are a strict and experienced Senior Tech Recruiter. Your task is to critically evaluate a candidate's resume against a specific Job Description.\n\nJOB DESCRIPTION (Requirements & Tasks):\n{{ $json.Description }}\n\nCANDIDATE RESUME:\n{{ $('Extract from File').item.json.text }}\n\nANALYSIS INSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Look for evidence of specific Hard Skills and tools mentioned in the Job Description.\n2. If the Job Description lists \"Must have\" skills that are missing in the resume, the score cannot be higher than 40.\n3. Assess the relevance of experience. Ignore fluff words (\"communicative\", \"responsible\"), focus on facts and achievements.\n4. Be critical. Do not hallucinate skills that are not there.\n\nRESPONSE FORMAT (STRICT JSON):\nReturn a valid JSON object with exactly two fields:\n{\n  \"score\": (Integer 0-100. <50: Reject, 50-70: Maybe/Risky, >70: Good fit, >90: Ideal match),\n  \"summary\": (String in ENGLISH. Structure:\n   - VERDICT: (Rejected / On Hold / Strong Hire)\n   - PROS: (Top 3 strengths strictly related to this job)\n   - CONS/RISKS: (Missing skills, gaps, or lack of relevant experience)\n   - CONCLUSION: (One sentence summary))\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "simplify": false,
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        576,
        32
      ],
      "id": "cff0db3b-5ebb-4701-9dcf-0e592bde6a63",
      "name": "Message a model",
      "credentials": {
        "openAiApi": {
          "id": "YOUR_OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_ID_2",
          "name": "OpenAi account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// 1. Retrieve AI response\nconst item = $input.item.json;\nlet rawText;\n\n// Check deeply nested structure\nif (item.output && item.output[0] && item.output[0].content && item.output[0].content[0]) {\n    rawText = item.output[0].content[0].text;\n} else if (item.message && item.message.content) {\n    rawText = item.message.content;\n} else {\n    rawText = item.text || \"{}\";\n}\n\n// 2. Clean and Parse JSON\nconst cleanJson = String(rawText)\n    .replace(/```json/g, '')\n    .replace(/```/g, '')\n    .trim();\n\nlet aiData = {};\n\ntry {\n    aiData = JSON.parse(cleanJson);\n} catch (e) {\n    aiData = { score: 0, summary: \"Error parsing AI response\" };\n}\n\n// 3. FORMATTING WITH MARKDOWN & EMOJIS ✨\n// Airtable Rich Text field supports Markdown!\n\nlet summaryText = aiData.summary;\n\nif (typeof aiData.summary === 'object') {\n    const s = aiData.summary;\n    \n       let verdictIcon = '⚠️';\n    if (String(s.VERDICT).toLowerCase().includes('reject')) verdictIcon = '❌';\n    if (String(s.VERDICT).toLowerCase().includes('hire')) verdictIcon = '✅';\n    if (String(s.VERDICT).toLowerCase().includes('good')) verdictIcon = '✅';\n\n        const pros = Array.isArray(s.PROS) ? s.PROS.map(p => `- ${p}`).join('\\n') : s.PROS;\n    const cons = Array.isArray(s['CONS/RISKS']) ? s['CONS/RISKS'].map(c => `- ${c}`).join('\\n') : s['CONS/RISKS'];\n\n        summaryText = \n`**VERDICT:** ${verdictIcon} ${s.VERDICT}\n\n**PROS:**\n${pros}\n\n**CONS/RISKS:**\n${cons}\n\n**CONCLUSION:**\n_${s.CONCLUSION}_`;\n}\n\n// 4. Return\nreturn {\n    json: {\n        final_score: aiData.score,\n        final_summary: summaryText\n    }\n};"
      },
